* Deploy the etcd chart with the following command:

    > NOTE: Remember that MY-RELEASE is a placeholder, replace it with the name you want to give to the deployment or add the *--generate-name* parameter to automatically generate a name.

        $ helm install MY-RELEASE bitnami/etcd
